dct_description_sm: Foiben'ny Taosarintanin' i Madagasikara [F.T.M.], Institut National de Géodésie et cartographie.
Relief represented by contours, points and shadows.
Includes map of administrative limits, table of base maps and definitive editions in topographic set.
